query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-room',
'android-webview',
'discord.js',
'field',
'greatest-n-per-group',
'ibm-mobilefirst',
'inner-product-space',
'interpolation',
'ios7',
'microservices',
'runtime-error',
'sequelize.js',
'serial-port',
'stripe-payments',
'vlookup')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math',
'stackoverflow',
'tex')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Benefactor',
'Cleanup',
'Disciplined',
'Good Answer',
'Self-Learner',
'Tag Editor',
'Talkative',
'Yearling') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
